title: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet) is not returning expected output
description: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet) is not returning expected output. The current output is "MySomeClass".
OB: Currently, the code is returning the output "MySomeClass", but I expect it to return the output "MySomeClass". It seems that the code is not yet implemented according to the Servlet 3.0 spec. On Glassfish 3.0, the code works fine.
EB: The code should be implemented according to the Servlet 3.0 spec to return the correct output.
SR: To resolve this bug, the code should be modified to correctly implement the Servlet 3.0 spec and return the expected output.
